official_title: A bill relating to the dutiable status of manganese ore, including ferruginous manganese ore, and manganiferous iron ore.

summary.text: Revises the duty status of manganese ore, including ferruginous manganese ore and manganiferous iron ore on the tariff schedules of the United States. (Amends 19 U.S.C. 1202)
